Net sales for the three months rose to Dollars 514m from Dollars 474m in the
corresponding period a year ago.
On the same basis, earnings for the full nine months rose to Dollars 165m
from Dollars 132m a year ago while net sales increased to Dollars 1.42bn
from Dollars 1.34bn.
