<HEADLINE>
FT  26 OCT 93 / Observer: Off piste
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Amid the fun, fashion and glamour of the Daily Mail's international ski show
at London's Olympia this week, there is a sobering note. At a stand
overlooking the artificial ski slope, The Will Partnership offers
'professional will drafting'. Clearly, some runs are not called The Widow
Maker for nothing.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
