Clean and efficient energy technologies                   1050   (9.6%)
Nuclear safety and security                                495   (4.5%)
Controlled thermo-nuclear fusion                           980   (9.0%)
Research for a European transport policy                   280   (2.6%)
Socio-economic research                                    125   (1.1%)
Co-operation with third countries &amp; int'l organisations    790
