<HEADLINE>
FT  25 OCT 93 / Observer: Sic
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
What embarrassed Commonwealth officials have termed a 'misunderstanding' has
provided an intimate glimpse into the lives of the leaders attending the
organisation's biennial conference in Cyprus. Journalists paging through the
official list of delegates were astonished to find copious notes on the
