FT  25 OCT 93 / Construction Contracts: Sunley posts two new deals
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE SUNLEY TURRIF GROUP has gained two Royal Mail contracts totalling Pounds
11m.
The first involves the Pounds 5.6m conversion and fitting-out of two
buildings, alterations and fitting-out of a third building and the
